{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act28side", "eventName": "不義之財", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "CV-6", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "獵人之夜", "storyInfo": "雷蛇小隊拒絕了銀行的動武命令，選擇站在民眾的一邊，潔西卡也因為“橋夾”克里夫對當地民眾的冷淡態度而深感失望。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_ltroom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness02_intro", "key": "$darkness02_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "廣袤的拓荒區還潛藏著相當的發展潛力，我們衷心歡迎那些才華得不到施展的公民前往拓荒區。", "name": "訪談嘉賓"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而對那些堅守自己家鄉的人，我們也為他們準備了地塊再開發計劃。", "name": "訪談嘉賓"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "地塊再開發計劃？", "name": "主持人"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對於一些產業落後的地塊，我們制定了令其煥然一新的再開發計劃。州政府吸引的高科技企業將利用這些寶貴的地塊發展高新產業。", "name": "訪談嘉賓"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "令人振奮的消息！我想這些地塊的居民已經迫不及待要見證光明的未來了。", "name": "主持人"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "州政府已經為數個地塊制定了再開發計劃，例如貝斯伍德鎮、戴德霍斯鎮、達維鎮……", "name": "訪談嘉賓"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不知道這些地塊上有沒有我們的觀眾呢？這對他們來說應該是新年的第一個好消息！", "name": "主持人"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "42_g9_modernoffice", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_176", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_176", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "克里夫先生，一想到此時能有機會親眼目睹巴倫基地的壯觀，我的心情就很激動。", "name": "銀行行長"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您太客氣了……和貴行這樣的企業合作才是我們的幸運。", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#8$1"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_176", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，克里夫先生，如果可能的話，有些在拓荒地的業務，我們依然想要繼續雙方的合作。", "name": "銀行行長"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這也正是我們的想法。", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#8$1"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_176", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "和您談話的過程總是很愉快，希望這種狀態能一直保持下去。畢竟拖拽也是個漫長的過程，直到春天徹底雪融，我們才能互道分別。", "name": "銀行行長"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那可真的是太短暫了，我會為此感到遺憾——", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#8$1"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "Stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "克里夫先生！克里夫先生！", "name": "潔西卡"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$doorknockquite"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "克里夫先生，請開開門，我有很緊急的事情要向你匯報。", "name": "潔西卡"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果您有任何合作上的需要，可以隨時聯繫——", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#8$1"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "開開門，求你了，事情真的很緊急！克里夫先生！！", "name": "潔西卡"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_176", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……看來您有些要緊事？", "name": "銀行行長"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請您稍等。", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$1"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_glassdooropen"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#11$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$formal_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "潔西卡，你來做什麼？誰讓你在我門口大吼大叫的？", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#6$1"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉，克里夫先生，潔西卡小姐要匯報的事情的確緊急。", "name": "秘書"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那就快說。", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#6$1"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那位先生……", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_176"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "克里夫先生，請問我可以借用一下您的洗手間嗎？", "name": "銀行行長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_176"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請用。", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#8$1"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#1$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "到底出了什麼事，要你來敲我的門？", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$1"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "銀行拿著州政府的授權書，要求我們對人群動手。", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#11$1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你們動手了嗎？", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#10$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "至少在我離開時還沒有，現在的情況我、我不知……", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不……", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#11$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，我們不會動手。", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#11$1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好，我知道了，出去吧。", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$1"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#10$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那些居民要怎麼辦？", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這和你沒有關係。", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$1"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#10$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但您至少可以……", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果你聽不懂，我可以再說得更明確一點。", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$1"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#10$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這和你、和我，都沒有關係。", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#10$1"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是嗎……？", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#11$1"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那什麼與您有關係呢……銀行回報給您的高額酬勞，軍方額外賦予您的特殊權力？還是肆意將別人踩在腳下時，給您的那種……", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#11$1"}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "高人一等的快感？", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#11$1"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "克里夫眯起眼睛，上下打量著眼前突然有些陌生的傭兵。"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我九十多歲了，不會那麼輕易就感到快樂，潔西卡。", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#2$1"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那為什麼呢……與那些人為伍您能得到什麼呢？", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#11$1"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我很難不為此感到疑惑，在我看來……您為了得到那些，幾乎喪失了一切人性。", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#11$1"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#10$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "人性……這詞對我來說是有些遙遠了。作為黑鋼這家傭兵公司的老闆，那些美好的詞彙有什麼用？", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#10$1"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "反倒是你，潔西卡小姐，如果你那樣看重這些品質……那你來黑鋼做什麼呢？", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#10$1"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#10$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我……", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 117, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我記得你父親曾經和我講過，你留在這裡是想解決一些問題，保護一些東西……", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$1"}, {"id": 119, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是……", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然如此，你為什麼不去做警察、法官或者治安官？再不行入伍也可以，做個士兵保家衛國不好嗎？", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$1"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可你選擇了做傭兵，你選擇了一份用武力換取金錢的工作，一份伴隨著殺戮與暴力的工作，一份稱不上光彩也得不了榮譽的工作。", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$1"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你也不缺錢，潔西卡，那你到底是為了什麼呢？", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$1"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#14$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#14$1"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果你沒想清楚，我可以作為過來人，給你一個答案。", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$1"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "野心……為了我自己的野心，為了證明我自己不比哥哥姐姐差，為了證明我不是家族裡的……平庸之輩。", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#11$1"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以我來到了這裡。", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#11$1"}, {"id": 132, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不錯，非常清醒的自我認知。", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$1"}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以不要站在這裡指責我做生意的方式了，你的父親也是位優秀的生意人，你作為他的孩子，應該向他多學學。", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$1"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "成熟些，理智些，少感情用事些。", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$1"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "讓她離開，秘書，以後但凡是她來找我，恕不接待。", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#6$1"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……幾十年前你坐視朋友被俘虜，幾十年後你坐視一群人被趕出自己的家園。", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#11$1"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果這是你口中所謂的成熟的、理智的、不感情用事的選擇。", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#11$1"}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那我寧願一輩子幼稚……一輩子只是平庸的傻瓜。", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#11$1"}, {"id": 142, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "潔西卡小姐，現在請你離開。", "name": "秘書"}, "figure_art": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#11$1"}, {"id": 144, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別動我……我會自己走。", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#11$1"}, {"id": 146, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "-200,0", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_glassdoorclose"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#7$1"}, {"id": 156, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_176", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看來您的事務已經處理好了，克里夫先生。", "name": "銀行行長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_176"}, {"id": 162, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒錯，行長先生。", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$1"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，我剛剛聽說了個消息，一個很不好很不好的消息。", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$1"}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的屬下，在銀行門口，給我的屬下，下達了開火的命令。", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$1"}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "未經請示，未經許可。", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$1"}, {"id": 167, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_176"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這有什麼不對嗎，克里夫先生？", "name": "銀行行長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_176"}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們有政府的授權，那支小隊又是您派給我們的，在事態緊急，需要強硬處理的時候，我想，一些詳細手段沒必要一一向您匯報。", "name": "銀行行長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_176"}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您放心，我們的人有分寸。但情況緊急，我們也肯定是將自己的需求放在首位。", "name": "銀行行長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_176"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "Stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "行長先生，你沒明白我在說什麼。", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#10$1"}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這消息很不好，不是對我來講，而是對於你。", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#10$1"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_176"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您……您在開玩笑。", "name": "銀行行長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_176"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_gunload"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有誰能越過我去指揮我的人，如果你還想我們以後能和睦相處的話，這句話我希望你能牢牢記住。", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#6$1"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "42_g4_bank", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$ponder_intro", "key": "$ponder_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1039_1#1$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1041_1#1$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1041_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那一疊文件你分類好了嗎？", "name": "銀行經理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1041_1#1$1"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1039_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我正在看……馬上、馬上就好了。", "name": "西爾維婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1039_1#1$1"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那個……我剛剛看到了一份股份質押文件，明明里昂·特雷門的股份是不久前才賣掉的……", "name": "西爾維婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1039_1#1$1"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是這份為他準備的空白合約卻出現在十幾年前的一堆文件裡。", "name": "西爾維婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1039_1#1$1"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且，這樣的文件不止一份，很多都放錯了……上面也沒人簽字。", "name": "西爾維婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1039_1#1$1"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1041_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不是放錯了，它們是提早準備好的。", "name": "銀行經理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1041_1#1$1"}, {"id": 203, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1039_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可十幾年前……有很多人甚至都還沒踏入過銀行。", "name": "西爾維婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1039_1#8$1"}, {"id": 205, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1041_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "西爾維婭，我們有一套專業的精算系統，一點貸款利息我們可不會放在眼裡。", "name": "銀行經理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1041_1#1$1"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們的目標是這裡的所有，一直以來都未曾改變。", "name": "銀行經理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1041_1#1$1"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1039_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這、這和當時說的不、不一樣……", "name": "西爾維婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1039_1#8$1"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1041_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也是，你離我們的核心業務是有點遠，不知道很正常，你應該更上進一點的。", "name": "銀行經理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1041_1#1$1"}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過現在我想……機會擺在面前，你應該沒有不珍惜的道理。", "name": "銀行經理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1041_1#1$1"}, {"id": 213, "prop": "Stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "42_g3_diner", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$warm_intro", "key": "$warm_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_doorbell", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4104_coldst_1#2$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.6}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4104_coldst_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "伍迪……你去哪裡了？", "name": "海倫娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4104_coldst_1#2$1"}, {"id": 229, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#10$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的胳膊怎麼了？", "name": "伍德洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1034_1#10$1"}, {"id": 231, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4104_coldst_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當了出頭鳥……最後挨教訓了。", "name": "海倫娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4104_coldst_1#4$1"}, {"id": 233, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "海倫娜，如果……我要離開這裡，你會和我一起走嗎？", "name": "伍德洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1034_1#5$1"}, {"id": 235, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4104_coldst_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……那傢伙和你說什麼了？", "name": "海倫娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4104_coldst_1#2$1"}, {"id": 237, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒說什麼……那些對話只不過再一次證明他依然是個面目可憎的混蛋。", "name": "伍德洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1034_1#7$1"}, {"id": 239, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4104_coldst_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但你當年卻為了那樣一個混蛋義無反顧離開拉特蘭，踏上哥倫比亞的土地，加入一場幾乎讓自己失去一切的戰爭。", "name": "海倫娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4104_coldst_1#9$1"}, {"id": 241, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "海倫娜，他描繪給我的理想太誘人了……成為英雄，帶領人們結束戰爭，在拉特蘭之外建立一片全新的樂土。", "name": "伍德洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1034_1#2$1"}, {"id": 243, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "何況，在一群腦袋混沌的青少年裡，那傢伙總是意志堅定，思緒清晰，難免會讓人想要追隨。", "name": "伍德洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1034_1#1$1"}, {"id": 245, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4104_coldst_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "伍迪……我明白，我都明白，我並不是說你是受騙了還是怎麼的。", "name": "海倫娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4104_coldst_1#3$1"}, {"id": 247, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4104_coldst_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只是想說，你並不需要為自己的過去而感到羞恥，無論你的旅途因何而始，最終都將你導向了如今。", "name": "海倫娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4104_coldst_1#2$1"}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "伍迪，那些錯誤鑄成了現在的你。", "name": "海倫娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4104_coldst_1#2$1"}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "偶爾可以回頭看看，但不要後悔，千萬不要。", "name": "海倫娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4104_coldst_1#2$1"}, {"id": 251, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "海倫娜……", "name": "伍德洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1034_1#5$1"}, {"id": 253, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4104_coldst_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "想不想跳支舞，伍迪，我可以教你。", "name": "海倫娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4104_coldst_1#1$1"}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在我十八歲的時候，一個傻乎乎的傢伙教會了我舞步，那傢伙是個徹頭徹尾的傻瓜，卻不妨礙我愛這支舞。", "name": "海倫娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4104_coldst_1#1$1"}, {"id": 256, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "其實，我會跳舞……", "name": "伍德洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1034_1#1$1"}, {"id": 258, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4104_coldst_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯……我怎麼一直都不知道？你什麼時候學的？", "name": "海倫娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4104_coldst_1#8$1"}, {"id": 260, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……很年輕的時候，我沒有告訴過你，你當然不知道。", "name": "伍德洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1034_1#1$1"}, {"id": 262, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4104_coldst_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在哪學的？", "name": "海倫娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4104_coldst_1#1$1"}, {"id": 264, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……在回宿舍的路上。", "name": "伍德洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1034_1#1$1"}, {"id": 266, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4104_coldst_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你想跳一支嗎？", "name": "海倫娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4104_coldst_1#1$1"}, {"id": 268, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……請吧，女士。", "name": "伍德洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1034_1#8$1"}, {"id": 270, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "42_g7_sonwydowntown_n", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_106_franka_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_107_liskam_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_106_franka_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "剛剛接到撤離通知時，你為什麼不走？", "name": "芙蘭卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_106_franka_1#1$1"}, {"id": 282, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_107_liskam_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一次違抗是違抗，兩次也是。", "name": "雷蛇"}, "figure_art": "avg_107_liskam_1#3$1"}, {"id": 284, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_106_franka_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘖……逞什麼能，連後來的那些小隊都知道，你是為了保證他們不對人群做出格的事。", "name": "芙蘭卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_106_franka_1#9$1"}, {"id": 286, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_106_franka_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "額頭還痛嗎？沒想到我們的同事對人群倒還好，對自己人真是一點情面也不留。", "name": "芙蘭卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_106_franka_1#11$1"}, {"id": 288, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_107_liskam_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我沒事，只是小傷口。", "name": "雷蛇"}, "figure_art": "avg_107_liskam_1#1$1"}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說到底也是我們抗命在先……我也不知道自己能做什麼，那就做些最基礎的事，保證每個人的安全。", "name": "雷蛇"}, "figure_art": "avg_107_liskam_1#1$1"}, {"id": 291, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_106_franka_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你已經做得很好了，優等生。", "name": "芙蘭卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_106_franka_1#11$1"}, {"id": 293, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_107_liskam_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "雷蛇"}, "figure_art": "avg_107_liskam_1#1$1"}, {"id": 295, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_106_franka_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……對了，我今天一直想和你說的，但是沒顧上……", "name": "芙蘭卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_106_franka_1#3$1"}, {"id": 297, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_107_liskam_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯？", "name": "雷蛇"}, "figure_art": "avg_107_liskam_1#1$1"}, {"id": 299, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_106_franka_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "新年快樂。", "name": "芙蘭卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_106_franka_1#7$1"}, {"id": 301, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_107_liskam_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "讓我看下錶……很遺憾，十二點已經過了，芙蘭卡。", "name": "雷蛇"}, "figure_art": "avg_107_liskam_1#9$1"}, {"id": 303, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_106_franka_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "又有什麼關係呢？", "name": "芙蘭卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_106_franka_1#3$1"}, {"id": 305, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_107_liskam_1#10$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "確實沒關係，我大概只是不爽你搶先說了……", "name": "雷蛇"}, "figure_art": "avg_107_liskam_1#10$1"}, {"id": 307, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_107_liskam_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "新年快樂。", "name": "雷蛇"}, "figure_art": "avg_107_liskam_1#9$1"}, {"id": 309, "prop": "Stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "42_g5_banktreasury", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$storyendjp_intro", "key": "$storyendjp_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1039_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "西爾維婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1039_1#1$1"}, {"id": 321, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "…………", "name": "西爾維婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1039_1#1$1"}, {"id": 322, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "厚重的鐵門緊緊闔起，機關彈動，發出沉悶的碰撞聲，隔絕了從門後揮發出的油墨味。"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那是一種令人如痴如醉的味道。"}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗅到它，人們便會產生美妙的錯覺，一切渴望將唾手可得，一切遺憾能彌合補償。"}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1039_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你想要的……到底是什麼？", "name": "西爾維婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1039_1#8$1"}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而你又在為了什麼……而感到遺憾呢？", "name": "西爾維婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1039_1#8$1"}, {"id": 329, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1039_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……西爾維婭。", "name": "西爾維婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1039_1#2$1"}, {"id": 331, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "keep": "true", "initamount": 0.0, "amount": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "42_g6_sonwydowntown_d", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "期末又是第一……哎呀，我是怎麼生出你這樣聰明的孩子的，西拉，我真是太為你驕傲了。", "name": "溫柔的聲音"}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "42_g7_sonwydowntown_n", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真的嗎，西拉？那可是哥倫比亞最好的金融系啊……天吶，我的女兒居然考上了！西拉，我為你自豪，說多少遍都不夠。", "name": "溫柔的聲音"}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "29_g8_alley_n", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "西拉，你確定你要回家鄉的銀行工作嗎？你知道……媽媽不想因為自己的身份影響你的選擇，尤其是在這樣重要的事上。", "name": "溫柔的聲音"}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我為你驕傲，我的孩子。", "name": "溫柔的聲音"}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_windows", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咳咳……咳咳，西拉……離開那裡吧，你可以找到別的工作的……媽媽……媽媽沒關係的。", "name": "溫柔的聲音"}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無論，無論你做什麼……媽媽，都會為你驕傲。", "name": "溫柔的聲音"}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就算……生命的盡頭，也是……一樣。", "name": "溫柔的聲音"}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "永遠……永遠為你驕傲。", "name": "溫柔的聲音"}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1039_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "amount": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "42_g5_banktreasury", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "媽媽……", "name": "西爾維婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1039_1#2$1"}, {"id": 372, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1039_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我……我希望，你能永遠為我驕傲。", "name": "西爾維婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1039_1#4$1"}, {"id": 374, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那是一種極具魔力的氣味，能將時間撥亂。"}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"conten